## ZFS snapshots
#*/15 * * * * root zfsnap.sh snapshot -rsSvz -p 15min-   -a 3d      pool rpool tank > /dev/null 2>&1
#@daily       root zfsnap.sh snapshot -rsSvz -p daily-   -a 3w      pool rpool tank
#@weekly      root zfsnap.sh snapshot -rsSvz -p weekly-  -a 3m      pool rpool tank
